#: ../../concepts.rst:2
msgid "核心概念"
msgstr "Core Concepts"

#: ../../concepts.rst:4
msgid ""
"本部分说明 AgentSociety 2 的系统结构与术语；首页 :doc:`index` "
"中的「研究背景与平台定位」从范式与协作角度概括了平台动机，此处侧重实现层面的组件关系。"
msgstr ""
"This section describes the system structure and terminology of "
"AgentSociety 2. The :doc:`index` section \"Research Background and "
"Platform Positioning\" covers motivation from paradigms and "
"collaboration; here the focus is implementation-level component "
"relationships."

#: ../../concepts.rst:7
msgid "架构概述"
msgstr "Architecture Overview"

#: ../../concepts.rst:9
msgid "AgentSociety 2 围绕三个主要组件构建："
msgstr "AgentSociety 2 is built around three main components:"

#: ../../concepts.rst:11
msgid ""
"**智能体 (Agents)**: 使用 LLM 与环境交互的自主实体（workspace 绑定的无状态 record，由 Ray Task "
"流式驱动）"
msgstr ""
"**Agents**: Autonomous entities that use LLMs to interact with "
"environments"

#: ../../concepts.rst:12
msgid "**环境模块 (Environment Modules)**: 定义模拟规则的可组合组件"
msgstr ""
"**Environment Modules**: Composable components that define simulation "
"rules"

#: ../../concepts.rst:13
msgid "**AgentSociety**: 管理智能体和环境的协调器"
msgstr "**AgentSociety**: Coordinator that manages agents and environments"

#: ../../concepts.rst:15
msgid ""
"智能体不直接持有 env / LLM / trace / replay 等运行时对象，而是经一个 ``ServiceProxy`` 容器接收共享 "
"服务句柄；环境路由跑在专用 Ray actor 里。详见 :doc:`architecture`。"
msgstr ""
"Agents do not directly own runtime objects such as env, LLM, trace, or "
"replay. Instead, they receive shared service handles through a "
"``ServiceProxy`` container; environment routing runs in a dedicated Ray "
"actor. See :doc:`architecture`."

#: ../../concepts.rst:35
msgid "完整系统架构"
msgstr "Full System Architecture"

#: ../../concepts.rst:115
msgid "智能体-环境接口"
msgstr "Agent-Environment Interface"

#: ../../concepts.rst:117
msgid "智能体通过两个主要方法与环境交互："
msgstr "Agents interact with environments through two main methods:"

#: ../../concepts.rst:119
msgid "**ask()**: 查询或观察环境状态"
msgstr "**ask()**: Query or observe environment state"

#: ../../concepts.rst:120
msgid "**intervene()**: 修改环境状态"
msgstr "**intervene()**: Modify environment state"

#: ../../concepts.rst:122
msgid "这个统一接口允许智能体与任何环境模块自然通信。"
msgstr ""
"This unified interface allows agents to communicate naturally with any "
"environment module."

#: ../../concepts.rst:125
msgid "@tool 装饰器"
msgstr "The @tool Decorator"

#: ../../concepts.rst:127
msgid "环境模块通过 ``@tool`` 装饰器公开其功能："
msgstr ""
"Environment modules expose their functionality through the ``@tool`` "
"decorator:"

#: ../../concepts.rst:145
msgid "**参数：**"
msgstr "**Parameters:**"

#: ../../concepts.rst:147
msgid "``readonly`` (bool): 函数是否修改状态 * ``True`` = 只读观察 * ``False`` = 修改环境"
msgstr ""
"``readonly`` (bool): Whether the function modifies state * ``True`` = "
"read-only, can be used in queries * ``False`` = modifies state, can be "
"used in interventions"

#: ../../concepts.rst:151
msgid ""
"``kind`` (str): 用于优化的函数类别 * ``\"observe\"``: 单参数观察 * ``\"statistics\"``: "
"聚合查询（无参数） * ``None``: 常规工具"
msgstr ""
"``kind`` (str): The type of tool * ``\"observe\"``: Single-parameter "
"observations (requires readonly=True) * ``\"statistics\"``: Aggregate "
"queries (no parameters, requires readonly=True) * ``None`` or omitted: "
"Regular tool (any signature, any readonly value)"

#: ../../concepts.rst:157
msgid "CodeGenRouter"
msgstr "CodeGenRouter"

#: ../../concepts.rst:159
msgid "CodeGenRouter 通过以下方式将智能体连接到环境模块："
msgstr "CodeGenRouter connects agents to environment modules by:"

#: ../../concepts.rst:161
msgid "从环境模块中提取工具签名"
msgstr "Extracting tool signatures from environment modules"

#: ../../concepts.rst:162
msgid "根据智能体输入生成调用适当工具的代码"
msgstr "Generating code to call appropriate tools based on agent input"

#: ../../concepts.rst:163
msgid "在沙盒环境中安全执行代码"
msgstr "Safely executing code in a sandboxed environment"

#: ../../concepts.rst:164
msgid "将结果返回给智能体"
msgstr "Returning results to the agent"

#: ../../concepts.rst:166
msgid "这种方法允许智能体与任何环境模块组合交互，而无需更改代码。"
msgstr ""
"This approach allows agents to interact with any combination of "
"environment modules without code changes."

#: ../../concepts.rst:169
msgid "路由器选择"
msgstr "Router Selection"

#: ../../concepts.rst:171
msgid "``RouterBase`` 有多个实现，可按需替换："
msgstr "``RouterBase`` has multiple implementations that can be swapped as needed:"

#: ../../concepts.rst:173
msgid "``CodeGenRouter`` （默认）：生成调用代码并在沙盒执行，带 AST 守卫与缓存。"
msgstr ""
"``CodeGenRouter`` (default): generates call code and executes it in a "
"sandbox, with AST guards and caching."

#: ../../concepts.rst:174
msgid "``ReActRouter``：ReAct 式工具选择。"
msgstr "``ReActRouter``: ReAct-style tool selection."

#: ../../concepts.rst:175
msgid "``PlanExecuteRouter``：先规划再执行。"
msgstr "``PlanExecuteRouter``: plan first, then execute."

#: ../../concepts.rst:176
msgid "``TwoTierReActRouter`` / ``TwoTierPlanExecuteRouter``：两级路由，适合大工具集。"
msgstr ""
"``TwoTierReActRouter`` / ``TwoTierPlanExecuteRouter``: two-tier routing "
"for large tool sets."

#: ../../concepts.rst:177
msgid "``SearchToolRouter``：以检索方式选择工具。"
msgstr "``SearchToolRouter``: selects tools through retrieval."

#: ../../concepts.rst:179
msgid "生产环境下路由跑在专用 Ray actor（``EnvRouterProxy``）里，详见 :doc:`architecture`。"
msgstr ""
"In production, routing runs in a dedicated Ray actor "
"(``EnvRouterProxy``); see :doc:`architecture`."

#: ../../concepts.rst:182
msgid "工具类别"
msgstr "Tool Categories"

#: ../../concepts.rst:184
msgid "**观察工具** (``readonly=True``, ``kind=\"observe\"``)"
msgstr "**Observation Tools** (``readonly=True``, ``kind=\"observe\"``)"

#: ../../concepts.rst:186
msgid "具有单个 ``agent_id`` 参数的智能体特定观察："
msgstr "Agent-specific observations with a single ``agent_id`` parameter:"

#: ../../concepts.rst:195
msgid "**统计工具** (``readonly=True``, ``kind=\"statistics\"``)"
msgstr "**Statistics Tools** (``readonly=True``, ``kind=\"statistics\"``)"

#: ../../concepts.rst:197
msgid "没有参数的聚合查询（除了 ``self``）："
msgstr "Aggregate queries with no parameters (except ``self``):"

#: ../../concepts.rst:207
msgid "**常规工具**"
msgstr "**Regular Tools**"

#: ../../concepts.rst:209
msgid "具有任何签名的通用工具："
msgstr "General-purpose tools with any signature:"

#: ../../concepts.rst:220
msgid "工具类别层次结构"
msgstr "Tool Category Hierarchy"

#: ../../concepts.rst:246
msgid "智能体-环境交互流程"
msgstr "Agent-Environment Interaction Flow"
